### POST /services/activities/tours

This endpoint is used to create a new tour activity.

#### Request Body

- `name` (text): The name of the tour.

- `description` (text, nullable): A brief description of the tour.

- `refund_rate` (text): The refund rate for the tour (should be between 0 and 100).

- `allow_points` (text): Indicates whether or not points are allowed for the tour.

- `photos[]`

- `guide_id` (text): The ID of the guide for the tour.

- `takeoff_date` (text): The date of the tour takeoff.

- `duration` (text): The duration of the tour.


#### Response (201 - Created)

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "id": {
      "type": "number"
    },
    "name": {
      "type": "string"
    },
    "description": {
      "type": "string"
    },
    "refund_rate": {
      "type": "string"
    },
    "upfront_rate": {
      "type": "string"
    },
    "allow_points": {
      "type": "boolean"
    },
    "photos": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "id": {
            "type": "number"
          },
          "image": {
            "type": "string"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "sites": {
      "type": "array"
    },
    "tickets": {
      "type": "array"
    },
    "guide": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "id": {
          "type": "number"
        },
        "name": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "bio": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "avatar": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "likes": {
          "type": "number"
        },
        "email": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "liked": {
          "type": "boolean"
        },
        "is_popular": {
          "type": "boolean"
        }
      }
    },
    "takeoff_date": {
      "type": "string"
    },
    "end_date": {
      "type": "string"
    },
    "duration": {
      "type": "string"
    }
  }
}

